        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/44108893-the-confessor">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3098312195" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11757115654848840220"><strong>A Great Thriller</strong><br/><br/>A fast paced story of Vatican intrigue, with the Pope and other lives hanging in the balance. <br/><br/>Great characters that are easy to relate with. Accurate in Roman Catholic detail. <br/><br/>This is the best of the series thus far.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


