    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2283659636" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11311233773493202866">Yep, I had read this book previously, I knew for sure when Gabriel met Chiara in Vienna. I didn&apos;t remember how it ended, so maybe it didn&apos;t make a big impression, but I still enjoyed it.</span>
  <span id="freeText11311233773493202866" style="display:none">Yep, I had read this book previously, I knew for sure when Gabriel met Chiara in Vienna. I didn't remember how it ended, so maybe it didn't make a big impression, but I still enjoyed it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11311233773493202866" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
