<span id="freeTextContainer2909883001998300360">Once again, our hero Gabriell Allon is called back to investigate the murder of a Jewish professor named Benjamin Stern in Munich. It seemed he was not killed for being a jews but for his current research on the Holocaust on Jewish people. A powerful secret society Crux Vera is behind it and their aim to defend the reputation and power of the Catholic church at all cost. Not as good as the first two books but still enjoyed it.</span>

          </span>
